      <title>投资者关注美联储利率前景，黄金在清淡交投中上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/iron-ore-recoups-some-losses-as-steel-mills-restock-over-winter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者在消化好坏参半的国内就业数据，同时考虑美联储利率变动的前景，黄金在美国假日交易清淡中上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/iron-ore-recoups-some-losses-as-steel-mills-restock-over-winter</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 03:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券收益率攀升，股市反弹后失去动力：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[假期后市场平静，股市下跌，债券收益率上升，失业救济申请数据好坏参半，但这并未改变人们对美联储利率前景的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 23:57:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价因中国刺激计划和美国库存下降而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-26</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受中国财政刺激措施和美国行业报告预示国内库存再次下降的推动，油价在清淡的假日交易中小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-26</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 23:32:45 GMT</pubDate>
